description: Welcome to 361 W 4th #1 in the desirable west side of South Boston. This 2 bed 2 full bath floor plan will check all the boxes with DIRECT ELEVATOR ACCESS to unit and GARAGE PARKING! Upon entry, your eye will be quick to catch the expansive and open floor plan of this 1287 sq. ft unit featuring oversized windows and high ceilings. The kitchen is a chef’s dream featuring Viking appliances, ample cabinet space and an oversized island perfect for entertaining. The living room/dining room space is sizable, leaving room for multiple furniture configurations and a fireplace for winter nights. Plus, enjoy the front deck for grilling on summer nights! The primary bedroom has an en suite bath & large walk-in closet boasting custom built-ins. Enjoy a second deck off of the primary bedroom to provide some outdoor privacy. All of this and in unit laundry make this unit a must see with close proximity to all of South Boston’s favorite bars and restaurants!
